title._content: Marine Ag Program Captain Harry Mahan, Corporal Dwight Moser, and Chet Enman

description._content: Original Collection: Extension Service Photographic Collection Item Number: P062:110 Image Description: Sponsors of the Marine Corps Agricultural Project: Cpt. Harry Mahan, Cpl. Dwight Moser, and Chet Enman of the Klamath Jr. Farmers are standing before a field of carrots. Photo was used in the Klamath Annual Report-1945, page 36a.
